{
  "name": "Snowflake Revenue Command Center",
  "version": "0.2.0",
  "description": "Governed Snowflake + Domo revenue command center. Snowflake is the intelligence plane (Horizon + semantic views + Cortex Analyst/Agent + native ML + Hybrid Tables); Domo is the delivery + action plane. A live Code Engine bridge (package SnowflakeRevenueCommandCenter, key-pair JWT via Domo-managed account 148 / DOMO_CE_USER) powers Forecast Home, Cortex Analyst, Cortex Agent Queue, Snowflake ML inference, Hybrid Table ops, approval writeback, Horizon governance parity, and Cloud Amplifier registration.",
